                    Bulas oficiais
                </span>
                <span class="lp-badge">
                    <svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="#004d40" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-3 3-3-3z"/></svg>
